      "docs": "<p>The CancelJob operation cancels an unfinished job.</p> <note> <p>You can only cancel a job that has a status of <code>Submitted</code>. To prevent a pipeline from starting to process a job while you're getting the job identifier, use <a>UpdatePipelineStatus</a> to temporarily pause the pipeline.</p> </note>"
